# SvelteKit build output synced into webdist/ by `make sync-web` / Docker.
# The directory is a pure build artifact — nothing in it is ever committed.
# The SPA is embedded in the binary only when -tags embed_spa is passed
# (i.e. `make build` and the Docker image). A bare `go build ./...` or
# `make build-go` uses the in-code stub from spa_noembed.go instead.
internal/httpx/webdist/
